reviews.review_text: a birthday show for me Last time I saw Jerry alive.  Days between

Surprisingly good show!! This one caught me off guard!  This definitely is a great show for mid 90s.  The energy, especially toward the end, is great.  Throwing Stones is sublime - definitely worth a listen.   NFA/USB strong as well.
Front Row! Was very surprised to receive front row mail order for this one. Jerry hit every note of every song. Good Times!
